---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
import { Navbar } from '../components/Navbar.jsx'
import { Footer } from '../components/Footer.jsx'
import { ScrollUpButton } from '../components/ScrollUpButton.jsx'
---

<Layout title="Custom Cut and Sew – High-Volume, Full-Scale Production" Description="High-quality blank apparel for customization. T-shirts, hoodies, hats & more—perfect for embroidery, screen printing & DTG. Bulk orders available!">
  <Navbar client:load />
  <div class="container mx-auto p-4">
  <h1>Custom Cut and Sew – High-Volume, Full-Scale Production</h1>
  <div class="image-text-container">
  <figure class="image-wrapper">
    <img
      src="/embroidery/INVICTUS-Embroidered-Cap-Los-Angeles.jpg"
      alt="Custom Cut and Sew – High-Volume, Full-Scale Production"
      width="500"
      height="500"
    />
    <figcaption>Custom Cut and Sew – High-Volume, Full-Scale Production</figcaption>
  </figure>
  <div class="text-content">
  <p> <p>At <strong>E&R Unlimited</strong>, we specialize in <strong>high-volume, custom cut and sew</strong> services, offering <em>full-package production</em> for both small and big brands. Whether you're an emerging designer or an established company, we provide the expertise and resources to bring your vision to life.</p></p>
</div></div>
<section>
        <h2>Comprehensive Cut and Sew Services</h2>
        <p>Our <strong>cut and sew production</strong> includes everything you need for a seamless manufacturing experience:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Pattern making</strong> – Professional patterns tailored to your designs</li>
            <li><strong>Fabric cutting</strong> – Precision cutting for consistency and quality</li>
            <li><strong>Samples and prototypes</strong> – Get the perfect fit before mass production</li>
            <li><strong>Full-scale production</strong> – Efficient manufacturing for bulk orders</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We require a <strong>50-piece order minimum</strong>, ensuring efficiency while maintaining premium craftsmanship.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Athletic Wear Experts</h2>
        <p>We excel in creating <strong>athletic wear</strong>, including <em>t-shirts, hoodies, leggings, sports bras, shorts, and swimwear</em>. Our team understands the importance of <strong>durability, comfort, and performance</strong>, delivering products that meet industry standards.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Custom Apparel Embellishment Services</h2>
        <p>Beyond production, we also offer <strong>custom clothing embellishment services</strong>. Once your garments are manufactured, we can enhance them with:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Embroidery</li>
            <li>Screen printing</li>
            <li>Direct-to-garment (DTG) printing</li>
            <li>And more – all under one roof!</li>
        </ul>
        <p>With <strong>over 30 years of experience</strong>, we take pride in providing a <em>full-package manufacturing solution</em> that streamlines your production process.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Start Your Custom Cut and Sew Project Today!</h2>
        <p>Looking for a reliable, high-volume cut and sew manufacturer? <a href="/contact">Contact us today</a> to discuss your project or get a <strong>FREE quote</strong>!</p>
    </section>
</div>
  <Footer />
  <ScrollUpButton client:load />
</Layout>